---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-9xl font-bold text-gray-200">404</h1>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 -mt-8">页面未找到</h2>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        抱歉，您访问的页面不存在。可能该页面已被删除或地址输入错误。
      </p>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <Button href="/" variant="primary" class="inline-block">
          返回首页
        </Button>
        
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          <p>您也可以尝试：</p>
          <div class="mt-2 space-x-4">
            <a href="/analyze" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">文本分析</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">登录</a>
            <a href="/auth/register" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">注册</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* 添加一些动画效果 */
  h1 {
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }
</style>